<!-- tplID:46341 网评中心理论频道、学术频道、党建频道文章页右侧最热文章 -->
<div class="m-hotArticle is_ssi" id="m-hotArticle">
	<h2>最热文章</h2>
	<ul>
	  <li>        <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-11/12/content_37670374.htm" target="_blank">发展全过程人民民主，回应人民诉求</a>        </div>	<span class="topThree">1</span></li>		
	  <li>       <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-11/05/content_37658874.htm" target="_blank">“帅哥，你们是什么民族？”</a>        </div>	<span class="topThree">2</span></li>		
	  <li>        <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-11/04/content_37656583.htm" target="_blank">文化自信为中国式现代化注入力量</a>        </div>	<span class="topThree">3</span></li>		
	  <li>        <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-11/01/content_37652512.htm" target="_blank">让世界看见景德镇御窑</a>        </div>	<span>4</span></li>		
	  <li>        <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-10/29/content_37644351.htm" target="_blank">健全因地制宜发展新质生产力体制机制</a>        </div>	<span>5</span></li>		
	  <li>       <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-10/28/content_37641603.htm" target="_blank">新质生产力赋能文化产业高质量发展</a>        </div>	<span>6</span></li>		
	  <li>        <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-10/28/content_37641684.htm" target="_blank">数字技术助推国家公园高水平建设</a>        </div>	<span>7</span></li>		
	  <li>       <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-10/28/content_37639110.htm" target="_blank">实现人与自然和谐共生的现代化</a>        </div>	<span>8</span></li>		
	  <li>        <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-10/25/content_37635995.htm" target="_blank">“大金砖合作”推动全球经济治理体系变革</a>        </div>	<span>9</span></li>		
	  <li>        <div>                      <a atremote href="https://theory.gmw.cn/2024-10/24/content_37633716.htm" target="_blank">庄立臻：跑好历史长河里的文化接力</a>        </div>	<span>10</span></li>		
	</ul>
